ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收人棕地又唔見你班左膠傳媒嘈<br />\n塊地有人耕田你就嘈<br />\n塊地有幾隻狗你又嘈"},{"pid":"d1a94cba0ea2788ffafd1beaeaca47c729e579a9","tid":804701,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"我理解係收左賠償後，若有任何事情都係閣下自理。就係因為影響到你，政府先賠償你，個賠償係包所有因搬遷引起嘅損失，你覺得賠償不足大可以一開始同政府傾，到依家講啲咁不負責任嘅野，居心叵測。"},{"pid":"84e0cbf46fc16c5e6d5bcc0cb24fcc5213232452","tid":804701,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08660f9adde2872b9daf49dbdc0311d7cc7971a4","tid":804701,"uid":184459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"成個北區咩野都關呢個江小姐事咁<br />\n做埋啲野呃like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔見佢做過啲咩實際野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"你就呃like"}]}